%TUTORIAL -------------  MVS Bulk Data Transfer Tutorial  ------------ T
+  Command%===>_ZCMD
%
%                    ---------------------------------------
%                    ×      Generating a Transaction       ×
%                    ---------------------------------------
+
+
+ An MVS/BDT transaction is generated by selecting Option%T+ from the MV
+ menu.
+
+ You will be requested to provide information about:
+
+    - the FROM dataset and its origin
+       - the dataset organization (PO or PS) if it cannot be determined
+    - the TO dataset and its origin
+       - necessary creation information if a NEW dataset
+    - a name for the transaction (optional)
+    - other options, as necessary
+
+ You will then be presented with an option panel for you to specify the
+ disposition of the transaction.
)PROC
 &ZUP = RBDT0000
)END
